{"tid":2422236,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國：中國製牛油火鍋底料危害健康 甚至導致死亡","createTime":"2021-02-25T05:04:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T05:39:43.000Z","uid":337052,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc58a10768214185d0eaa39af8ac9aa7c32957f","tid":2422236,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"自中國非法進口 美回收近10萬磅牛油火鍋底料<br />\n最新更新：2021/02/25 12:39<br />\n<br />\n（中央社華盛頓24日綜合外電報導）<span class=\"red\">美國農業部食品安全檢疫處22日宣布，發現有近10萬磅的牛油火鍋底料是從中國非法進口，其中有些運至紐約，已下令回收並要求零售與餐廳業者丟掉或辦理退款。</span><br />\n<br />\n美國國家廣播公司（NBC）報導，美國農業部食品安全檢疫處（Food Safety and Inspection Service）表示，<span class=\"red\">加州貿易公司GLG Trading將回收未經檢查從中國進口的9萬6810磅火鍋底料。</span><br />\n<br />\n爭議的焦點在於，名揚火鍋底料的3種口味中辣、微辣與特辣產品中含有牛油成分。<br />\n<br />\n美國農業部食品安全檢疫處發言人亞當斯（Mitch Adams）說：「將回收的產品上沒有聯邦檢驗標誌。」他又說，GLG Trading公司是在驗證時發現這個問題。<br />\n<br />\n食品安全檢疫處表示，這些產品被運至亞利桑那州、加州、夏威夷州、內華達州、紐約州與德州的零售業者與餐廳。<br />\n<br />\n目前沒有食用後引發不適的消息傳出，不過食品安全檢疫處表示，有這種產品的人應丟棄，或辦理退貨退費。<br />\n<br />\n食品安全檢疫處稱這是一級回收，代表<span class=\"red\">「這是危害健康的情況，使用這種產品有合理的可能性會導致嚴重與負面的健康後果，甚至是死亡」</span>。（譯者：張曉雯/核稿：徐睿承）1100225<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202102250113.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Faopl%2F202102250113.aspx&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFYMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=b0a367ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202102250113.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"8ea15daed3bac10f76e568c419b557935dbaa4d0","tid":2422236,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:06:16.000Z","msg":"口交部：石頭 腳 無中生有 借題發揮 不會得逞 政治化"},{"pid":"ee7d766d3e7147d2d4023470be0f91dbeb978bf3","tid":2422236,"uid":987,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"美國講食品健康，笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65b087891e6844875a3a6dd7693bf288f311f375","tid":2422236,"uid":325309,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ee7d766d3e7147d2d4023470be0f91dbeb978bf3","tid":2422236,"uid":987,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"美國講食品健康，笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:07:39.000Z","msg":"連美國都覺危害健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6119b4735394d60df0ea601f79106b8aa48be0c","tid":2422236,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:08:41.000Z","msg":"講咗咁多即係邊樣成分係違禁品或者有害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"6fab450d84b2f0b72313846813ad7b993665f364","tid":2422236,"uid":26329,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee7d766d3e7147d2d4023470be0f91dbeb978bf3","tid":2422236,"uid":987,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"美國講食品健康，笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"而家講緊非法入口未經檢查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你點知入面用咩造"},{"pid":"d99bba1bba668913984182cf5687394ec49cd8fd","tid":2422236,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:09:03.000Z","msg":"支那野假同大把科學元素，一早出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家美帝先醒，支那又贏"},{"pid":"9cae9b4c915e058824415851e1de455af6e13838","tid":2422236,"uid":257914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:20:36.000Z","msg":"火鍋底料  = 湯底?"},{"pid":"5b19d6150118917331c4c357e59379f3503bef2e","tid":2422236,"uid":218494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee7d766d3e7147d2d4023470be0f91dbeb978bf3","tid":2422236,"uid":987,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:06:33.000Z","msg":"美國講食品健康，笑撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"佢捉佢嘅原因係因為冇個個食衞logo，有嘅話就算屎都冇問題"},{"pid":"4d94e5abb1bd6144afcf1d4a88b71d23808ce2c2","tid":2422236,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6119b4735394d60df0ea601f79106b8aa48be0c","tid":2422236,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:08:41.000Z","msg":"講咗咁多即係邊樣成分係違禁品或者有害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:28:18.000Z","msg":"脂肪 膽固醇"},{"pid":"1eea5ec3673bea41b1330e066de911e2a053afe4","tid":2422236,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:28:58.000Z","msg":"新聞嚟？"},{"pid":"4767e220a938b2ba7642efb91faaf73e1d65d38c","tid":2422236,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:39:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">可能致死？ 全美下架回收近10萬磅中國製火鍋料底</span></strong><br />\n2021/02/25 07:25<br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/business/page/800/2021/02/25/php3kQPtu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fbusiness%2Fpage%2F800%2F2021%2F02%2F25%2Fphp3kQPtu.jpg&h=b096f6dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n近10萬磅中國製火鍋底料被召回。（圖擷取自FSIS官方網頁）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕<span class=\"red\">已經出口到美國的中國四川「名揚」（Ming Yang）火鍋底料，其中含有的牛脂成分被認為危害健康，甚至可能致死，美國食品安全檢查局（FSIS）下令全美下架及回收</span>，總數約96,810磅，由於冬天華人愛吃火鍋，這款麻辣火鍋料底下架，讓華人有點擔心吃不到家鄉味火鍋。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，遭FSIS下令回收的調味品已經進入美國，並分別運往亞利桑那州、加州、夏威夷、內華達州、紐約州和德州的超市及餐館銷售和使用。<br />\n<br />\nFSIS召回等級分I、II和III三級，此次名揚火鍋料被召回等級是I級（最高級），意思是「這是一種危害健康的產品，使用該產品有合理的可能性會導致嚴重的、不利的健康後果或死亡」。建議消費者不要食用，採取退貨或丟掉處理。<br />\n<br />\n據官方聲明，指這款火鍋料底的問題出在牛脂，中國既非美國評定的合格牛肉生產國，且這些產品全部沒有經過經過美國農業部食品安全檢驗局（FSIS）的複檢，不具聯邦檢查標記。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3448708\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3448708&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFYMqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=c8a9df21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3448708&h=8c586fa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3448708</a>"}]}